e.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/trace_billy_cyrus-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/trace_billy_cyrus-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>特雷斯·赛勒斯表示，他的父亲<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-ray-cyrus">比利·雷·赛勒斯</a>在恳求父亲“寻求帮助”后，正在对他“采取法律行动”。</p><p>本周早些时候（1 月 22 日），这位地铁站吉他手、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-cyrus">诺亚·赛勒斯</a>的哥哥在 Instagram 上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-ray-cyrus-family-are-genuinely-worried-about-him-says-trace-cyrus-3831363">分享了一封致父亲的公开信</a>，因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billy-ray-cyrus-disastrous-performance-at-trump-inauguration-3830691">他在特朗普就职典礼上的表演受到了广泛批评</a>。</p><p>这位乡村明星经历了一波技术故障，并被指控在自由舞会上假同步，而一些在线观众也质疑他目前的状态。</p><p> “可悲的是，我拼命想要成为的那个人，就像我现在几乎认不出的那样，”特雷斯写道。 “似乎这个世界已经打败了你，除了你之外，每个人都看得很清楚。” </p><figure id="attachment_3830695" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830695" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830695" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-ray-cyrus@2000x1270.jpg" alt="比利·雷·赛勒斯在自由女神就职舞会上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-ray-cyrus@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-ray-cyrus@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-ray-cyrus@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-ray-cyrus@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-ray-cyrus@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/billy-ray-cyrus@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830695" class="wp-caption-text">比利·雷·赛勒斯在自由女神就职舞会上表演。图片来源：Joe Raedle/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “你可能会对我发布这条消息感到不满，但此时我真的可以不在乎了。多年来我和女儿们一直真诚地担心你，但你却把我们所有人都推开了。”</p><p>他补充说，他“已经戒酒超过一年半了”，他直接对比利·雷说道：“我不知道你到底在挣扎什么，但我想我有一个很好的主意，而且如果您愿意敞开心扉并接受帮助，我很乐意帮助您。你知道如何联系我。在那一天到来之前，我会继续为你祈祷。”</p><p>现在，Trace 在 Instagram 上提供了最新消息，他在其中向父亲讲话，并表示他的信息“超越了爱”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFQkkxmOwX0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C52